19-11-17T16:37:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a0225f9095dbffc0ce2a73b332b03ef5f9c195c5","tid":1731220,"uid":241210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T16:38:03.000Z","msg":"Liked and retweeted"},{"pid":"e3ff27dc8299696c6f310d62f94bcbd9a15cce04","tid":1731220,"uid":248394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T16:38:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bca690e12524aeeaa3a5339a206d57de8e5c0943","tid":1731220,"uid":241210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T16:38:16.000Z","msg":"Shared"},{"pid":"7a392b7544b35e807b8bf8f9ed5a04fe7e143a75","tid":1731220,"uid":248394,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T16:38:19.000Z","msg":"轉到佢仆街"},{"pid":"c644ffee62a6c474f824c0a93c4d722f63ac4f73","tid":1731220,"uid":139677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T16:38:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"060fd1635a01af76b0c7f32fb34fff3003de90fb","tid":1731220,"uid":303641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T16:38:49.000Z","msg":"如果你宜家坐響屋企唔知做咩，又過唔到去救手足。<br />\n請每一個宜家即刻打呢段template比蔡英文，炸爆佢嘅fb同email，記住，呢場有可能系人道浩劫！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蔡總統：<br />\n<br />\n香港自六月起，烽煙不絕。台港同氣連枝，一直為香港發聲，港人不勝銘感。<br />\n<br />\n自十一月起，香港警察多次進入校園，中大二號橋之戰更是令無數港人徹夜難眠。今天（17/11），港警包圍香港理工大學，示威者退無可退，展現『不自由，無寧死』的精神。<br />\n<br />\n入夜，數百示威者仍身在理工校園，被重重圍困。此情此景，如八九年的中國，六四事件正在重現。<br />\n<br />\n我們已退無可退，為了避免人道災難的重現，懇請蔡總統向國際及港府施以壓力，台港並肩，共度劫難。<br />\n<br />\n鈞鑒"},{"pid":"8591d4421f64d856a668b1c5b6fab0a27748b96c","tid":1731220,"uid":241458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T16:39:06.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b52a8861a7a554d60b978ed2a2f1d47de3828cfc","tid":1731220,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T16:39:37.